    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "I was born [REDACTED] My father's name was",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "[REDACTED] I was a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "resident of Minnesota until I was six years old when my family moved to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Scobey, Montana, where they homesteaded. My grandfather, [REDACTED] b6",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "also homesteaded in Scobey, Montana, and became quite prominent in political",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "circles along with [REDACTED] the famous [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "I went to grade school and high school at Minot, North Dakota. I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "entered scouting at twelve years of age and achieved the rank of Eagle scout",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "before I was fourteen. My former scout executive was [REDACTED] now a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "[REDACTED] for the Boy Scouts in Kansas City, Kansas.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "As a boy, I was interested in athletics and was [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "[REDACTED] I entered the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "U. S. Olympic trials in [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "[REDACTED] I taught swimming and diving",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "at scout camps and the municipal pool in Minot, North Dakota. I went to the b6",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "University of Minnesota, where I swam and did fancy diving under [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "and also played football under [REDACTED] but upon entering college I",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "was unable to continue my football career because of an injured knee. My",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "high school football coach was [REDACTED] who is now the [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "[REDACTED] I had little or no finances, and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "my ambition in furthering my education in college was through my athletics.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "As a boy in Minot, North Dakota, I did a good deal of dog sled racing,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "In 1938 I went to work for [REDACTED] a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "manufacturer of automatic fire fighting apparatus. In 1939 I was made",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "[REDACTED] for them over a part of the western states, and in 1940 I b6",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "established my own [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "[REDACTED] I have been working as an [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "My flying experience started as a boy in Minot, North Dakota, where",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "I took my first flying lesson from [REDACTED] who was originally from",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Great Falls, Montana. Due to the high cost at that time, I was unable to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "continue my flying and did not fly of any great consequence until 1943. b6",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "I was given my pilot certificate by [REDACTED] senior CAA inspector of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Portland, Oregon, and for the last [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "covering my entire territory with same and flying from forty to one hundred",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "hours per month since. Due to the fact that I use an airplane entirely in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "my work, in January of this year I purchased a [REDACTED] airplane, which",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "is an airplane designed for high altitude take-offs and short rough field use.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "In the type of flying I do, it takes a great deal of practice and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "judgment to be able to land in most any cow pasture and get out without",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "injuring your airplane; the runways are very limited and the altitude is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "very high in some of the fields and places I have to go in my work. To",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "date, I have landed in 823 cow pastures in mountain meadows, and in over",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "a thousand hours a flat tire has been my greatest mishap.",
